      "rationale": "All three FEA implementations (FDA, Ansys, DePuy Synthes) operate under documented software quality management systems. Version control, regression testing, and change control procedures are in place. Achieved level exceeds required for this factor."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
