    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for Model Risk Level 3. The single deficiency in Test conditions (achieved level 2 vs. required level 3) is acknowledged; the assessment team determined that the ASTM F1717 standardized protocol provides sufficient constraint on test condition variability for the intended regulatory submission context, and that the overall credibility evidence supports an Accepted decision at Medium assurance level.",
